(142, 1, '2016-04-05 09:29:23', '2016-04-05 01:29:23', '<section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">       [espro-slider id=136]  </section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">       北京邮电大学国际学院志愿者协会（简称“国院志协”）是一个自我管理，自我服务的学生组织，承载着服务社会、服务广大师生、丰富校园生活、引领校园志愿思潮的重要职责。</section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section></section><section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">        国院志协目前是一个由四个部门组成的团体，部门设置健全，包括志愿服务部、外联部2个活动职能部门以及办公室、宣传部2个综合职能部门。</section><section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">        国院志协始终坚持“快乐志愿，快乐奉献”的理念，开展了爱心志愿行、志愿鸟巢、志愿首都博物馆、志愿北京海洋馆、GMIC、GITC、ITTC、S&amp;T技术交流大会、走进“红丝带之家”等一系列高质量的品牌活动，受众从孤寡老人、流浪小动物、孤残儿童、艾滋病患者等弱势群体，到全球各地游客和学术领域人才。</section><section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">       我们屡获称赞，作为唯一的高校志愿团队，国院志协被鸟巢授予“国家体育场（鸟巢）志愿工作支持单位” 称号，也光荣的成为了航空总医院的志愿合作伙伴。</section><section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">        荣誉在手，责任在肩，我们脚踏实地，我们自豪前行。 国际学院志愿者协会，一个意味着奉献、温暖和感恩的名字。从她成立之初，直到现在，也许她已经有些改变，志协精神却从没有变过，我们始终以无私奉献社会，传承志愿精神为己任，造就了如今充满着欢乐和温馨的国院志协。 奉献精神不灭，国院志协不息，前行之路上，我们越走越好！</section></section>', '简介', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '91-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-05 09:29:23', '2016-04-05 01:29:23', '', 91, 'http://tywings.ml:8090/index.php/2016/04/05/91-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(143, 1, '2016-04-05 09:35:13', '2016-04-05 01:35:13', '<section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">      <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-138" src="http://tywings.ml:8090/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/171007251055981189-302x227.jpg" alt="外联部" width="302" height="227" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-140" src="http://tywings.ml:8090/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/703169575948213899-302x151.png" alt="宣传部" width="302" height="151" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-139" src="http://tywings.ml:8090/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/680987111349394077-302x170.jpg" alt="办公室" width="302" height="170" /> <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-137" src="http://tywings.ml:8090/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/33978581010160810-302x169.jpg" alt="服务部" width="302" height="169" /></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">       北京邮电大学国际学院志愿者协会（简称“国院志协”）是一个自我管理，自我服务的学生组织，承载着服务社会、服务广大师生、丰富校园生活、引领校园志愿思潮的重要职责。</section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section></section><section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">        国院志协目前是一个由四个部门组成的团体，部门设置健全，包括志愿服务部、外联部2个活动职能部门以及办公室、宣传部2个综合职能部门。</section><section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">        国院志协始终坚持“快乐志愿，快乐奉献”的理念，开展了爱心志愿行、志愿鸟巢、志愿首都博物馆、志愿北京海洋馆、GMIC、GITC、ITTC、S&amp;T技术交流大会、走进“红丝带之家”等一系列高质量的品牌活动，受众从孤寡老人、流浪小动物、孤残儿童、艾滋病患者等弱势群体，到全球各地游客和学术领域人才。</section><section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">       我们屡获称赞，作为唯一的高校志愿团队，国院志协被鸟巢授予“国家体育场（鸟巢）志愿工作支持单位” 称号，也光荣的成为了航空总医院的志愿合作伙伴。</section><section></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI"></section></section><section class="tn-Powered-by-XIUMI">        荣誉在手，责任在肩，我们脚踏实地，我们自豪前行。 国际学院志愿者协会，一个意味着奉献、温暖和感恩的名字。从她成立之初，直到现在，也许她已经有些改变，志协精神却从没有变过，我们始终以无私奉献社会，传承志愿精神为己任，造就了如今充满着欢乐和温馨的国院志协。 奉献精神不灭，国院志协不息，前行之路上，我们越走越好！</section></section>', '简介', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '91-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-04-05 09:35:13', '2016-04-05 01:35:13', '', 91, 'http://tywings.ml:8090/index.php/2016/04/05/91-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
